{"tid":49702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣西男設陷阱電擊田鼠食用　反把親弟電死","createTime":"2016-12-22T01:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T04:27:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7157b7d2ed7b26f003373570abfcde8524a1fa2","tid":49702,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/photo/bkncn-20161222064907894-1222_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161222073739\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161222064907894-1222_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161222073739&h=dedd1827&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣西梧州市萬秀區夏郢鎮一名21廖姓男子，為了捕捉田鼠食用，在其舅舅家的農地安裝通電的鐵線，並在上周一（12日）展開「獵鼠行動」。不料，田鼠沒有捉到，卻反而電死了自己的弟弟。事發後，廖男向警方自首。而警方考慮廖男需照顧患重病的母親，讓他取保候審。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，廖男早在上年底已從網上購來電撃田鼠的設備。他與弟弟今年又將設備搬到舅舅家的農地，又布置了近400米長的鐵線，並在附近豎立起警示牌。事發當日，廖男將鐵線的電源接通後，便離開現場到舅舅家吃飯。不料當他再回到農地時，竟發現自己弟弟伏在地上的鐵線上一動不動。雖廖男已立即將弟弟救出送院，但為時已晚。 <br />\n<br />\n廖男供稱，他曾與弟弟一起在農地布線，也一起「電過老鼠」，對設備和鐵線的位置十分熟悉。因此，他弟弟很可能因為喝醉，不慎從石頭上滑倒，再摔在通電的鐵線上。"},{"pid":"34d0e45129eb0ab76c03ea19ac5a370251d06c45","tid":49702,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295d6e04983ac4e3dcb10273660930a106c9f683","tid":49702,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f13c1cfa30bf51f180827640ee40f27c295de5fb","tid":49702,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:53:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7de21100f64d6fee7565f87ae157eb25e2aebb81","tid":49702,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"誤中副車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624982b8b871ab37b37db1d01405c3358fcbadc0","tid":49702,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c9d70e0055f13c928ba4dcf5b4c01b5de700833","tid":49702,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:55:36.000Z","msg":"獵左隻烏鼠"},{"pid":"db727085c7ae3a49e1c4289a2eb6d97ab8e3c67c","tid":49702,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:57:28.000Z","msg":"無田鼠食<br />\n<br />\n但有親弟"},{"pid":"06730c002b191d2071710937402934a8ed33c469","tid":49702,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"其實有d懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強國人種狠毒唔係講笑<br />\n死左少個人分豬肉<br />\n<br />\n佢地屋企 農戶有地<br />\n佢老母已經病重  看描述 佢老豆應該都唔到"},{"pid":"91ab6adae456357de9b0876f3f2c3c868c25e3c0","tid":49702,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有d懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強國人種狠毒唔係講笑<br />\n死左少個人分豬肉<br />\n<br />\n佢地屋企 農戶有地<br />\n佢老母已經病重  看描述 佢老豆應該都唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n看錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係佢親戚塊地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過農村 佢地屋企有地呢個可能性都係有"},{"pid":"6dc19b051a82b09d2b84e1e8cfd744024f836ce0","tid":49702,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:05:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食得唔好晒呀喂</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616fa598c4f6a02f38ba82768943a704d8db0ec3","tid":49702,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"冚家炸田鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c863a149e140ea9cd6fb5517e4db88243ed411b","tid":49702,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl